metadata.Plot: The four Jennings brothers are Lawyers. When Al has a brother murdered, he goes after the murderer. He outdraws him but a witness says it was murder. Escaping the Sheriff he take refuge on a cattle ranch only to learn all the hands are rustlers. With a price on his head Al joins them and becomes an outlaw. His fame grows as does the reward for his capture.
metadata.Writer: George Bricker, Al J. Jennings, Will Irwin
metadata.Actors: Dan Duryea, Gale Storm, Dick Foran
